# Description: Showcase starting task work with ace-overseer and checking dashboard status
# Tags: ace-overseer,docs,getting-started

Output docs/demo/ace-overseer-getting-started.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 960
Set Height 540

Type "mise exec -- ace-overseer work-on --task 8q4.t.umu.1"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "mise exec -- ace-overseer status"
Enter
Sleep 3s
